                <h1>Sophomore year: 2015-2016</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/3dde643d-e49b-4930-a609-cf4dd6f7f500.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="President&#x20;Brodhead&#x20;announced&#x20;that&#x20;he&#x20;will&#x20;step&#x20;down&#x20;at&#x20;the&#x20;end&#x20;of&#x20;the&#x20;2016-17&#x20;year." class="w-100">
